{"tid":728484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[2018DSE]文科jj預自己15分左右 nursing有咩出路⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-07-03T20:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T21:51:08.000Z","uid":14746,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49e4c2236ce11989a7b95dfe150be67671e037ec","tid":728484,"uid":14746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T20:44:29.000Z","msg":"11號放榜 最差預自己15分左右⋯⋯(作最壞打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n如果數學得1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩途徑第時入翻護理行業<br />\n做到nurse就最好啦<br />\n想問下各位巴絲13-17分有咩nursing programme推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9d075f72132cac884496f5d3d0a02d9c68d4e3","tid":728484,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T20:57:34.000Z","msg":"ive"},{"pid":"9bbb9f88b9e06c2c1e6c2d608fc2e2295c4f0ecf","tid":728484,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T21:14:37.000Z","msg":"Nursing school"},{"pid":"da21f4b5fd3ee42fcdaf9bb843a1594c58fb4f8c","tid":728484,"uid":99086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T21:15:49.000Z","msg":"文科讀nursing搵自己黎搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c4b48af4626639115af2258d86635755151d3a","tid":728484,"uid":135645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T21:24:06.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦"},{"pid":"04d2c35e6d94c64aaa937436df6e61355c36c0ac","tid":728484,"uid":130308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T21:40:57.000Z","msg":"真心想讀nursing 好多可以揀啦 <br />\n前提係真係有心想讀 唔係嘅話都幾難捱<br />\n<br />\n你可以asso (hkuspace/hkcc) 搏升u<br />\n可以報nursing school<br />\nRN 就得HA 7月13截 (要有3322)<br />\nEN 就好多間 養和 葛量洪 St.Teresa 仁安 ou 浸會有兩個 一個係同中大搞嘅<br />\n<br />\n都大個啦 廢事乜都餵到入你口 截止日期 其他資料你自己再上網睇啦<br />\n<br />\n最後講多句 要讀有好多途經 但都真係辛苦嘅<br />\nSchool收都唔代表係一定畢到業<br />\n年中唔少讀唔掂 被踢<br />\n所以低分入到收你都唔好太開心 要努力啲"},{"pid":"7a39a